::'''Soda Animator:''' Let's keep going then: "Mr. Soda began to brew up a mysterious beverage. All of this was to (soothe the people's pain with sweetness/make a huge sum of money/use the soda to control the minds of the people)."
::'''Soda Animator:''' "But his behavior angered Boss Stone, who would not allow anyone to transgress on his turf. The vile Boss Stone used a trick to capture Mr. Soda, and tossed him into a prison cell."
::'''Soda Animator:''' "However, Mr. Soda had a stroke of great fortune. He was met with an opportunity for freedom not long after being imprisoned &mdash; Brother Hanu and his gang had caused a riot and the Compass, which was carrying Clockie on it, had just arrived in town."
